data.description: This 3-bed, 2-bath home on a tranquil wooded lot features a kitchen with granite counters. Gorgeous casement windows allow beauty of the outdoors and natural light to stream into the kitchen/dining area.  The entry level includes a bonus room which can be used as a home office. Upstairs, you'll find three bedrooms, with the primary bedroom offering a stunning full bathroom with a walk-in shower. I can't forget new roof installed last year & PVC piping recently replaced all the way to the road.  Geothermal unit recently serviced. The backyard is a private oasis with a patio overlooking the yard. Don't miss the chance to tour this gem!
